OL,3,CVisitors to Guernsey hospital asked to
OL,4,Ccheck symptoms after rise in illnesses
OL,6,FIslanders going to the Princess
OL,7,FElizabeth Hospital in Guernsey, as
OL,8,Fwell as those attending outpatient
OL,9,Fappointments, are being asked to check
OL,10,Fthey do not have symptoms of
OL,11,Fcontagious illness before visiting.
OL,13,FIt comes after an increase in the
OL,14,Fnumber with cold, flu and Covid-19 at
OL,15,Fthe hospital.
