OL,3,CVisitors to Guernsey hospital asked to
OL,4,Ccheck symptoms after rise in illnesses
OL,6,FA statement from Health and Social
OL,7,Fcare read: "There has recently been a
OL,8,Frise in the number of visitors to the
OL,9,FPEH campus presenting with symptoms of
OL,10,Fpotential illnesses such as cold, flu,
OL,11,FCovid and D&V (diarrhoea and vomiting
OL,12,Fbug).
OL,14,F"Visitors passing illnesses to those
OL,15,Falready on wards causes additional
OL,16,Frisks to patients. This is always true
OL,17,Fbut especially at this time of year
OL,18,Fwhen there is an increase in winter
OL,19,Fbugs."
